5
00:00:15,700 --> 00:00:21,500
SuperSoft is currently privately held and 100% equity financed.

6
00:00:21,500 --> 00:00:24,650
Its projected annual pre-tax cash flow

7
00:00:24,650 --> 00:00:29,060
